span> <span class="hps">la lumi&egrave;re.</span> <span class="hps">Gardez</span> <span class="hps">Tadapox</span> <span class="hps">hors de la port&eacute;e</span> <span class="hps">des enfants</span> <span class="hps">et loin des animaux</span><span>.</span></span></p><p><strong><span lang="fr">INFORMATION ADDITIVE:</span></strong></p><p>Les ingr&eacute;dients actifs: <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Tadalafil</span> <span class="hps">et</span> <span class="hps">Dapoxetine</span></span></p><p><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Tadapox</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">fonctionne</span> <span class="hps">pendant environ 36</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">heures apr&egrave;s la</span><span class="alt-edited"> prise.</span><br /><br /> <span class="hps">Tadapox</span> <span class="hps">(Tadalafil</span> <span class="hps">avec Dapoxetine</span><span>)</span> <span class="hps">est disponible en comprim&eacute;s</span> <span class="hps">qui contiennent</span> <span class="hps">20 mg de Tadalafil</span> <span class="hps">et</span> <span class="hps">60mg de Dapoxetine.</span> <span class="hps">Certains hommes</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">peuvent prendre</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">une petite dose de</span> <span class="hps">Tadapox</span> <span class="hps">(Cialis</span> <span class="hps">avec Dapoxetine</span><span>) en raison de</span> <span class="hps">troubles m&eacute;dicaux ou des</span> <span class="hps">m&eacute;dicaments</span> <span class="hps">qu'ils prennent.</span></span></p><p><strong>RENSEIGNEMENTS DE S&Eacute;CURIT&Eacute;</strong></p><p><strong><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Ne prenez pas</span> <span class="hps">Tadapox</span> <span class="hps">si:</span></span></strong></p><ul><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">vous &ecirc;tes allergique</span> <span class="hps">&agrave; un ingr&eacute;dient de</span> <span class="hps">Tadapox</span><span>.</span></span></li><li><