="hps">de ces</span> <span class="hps">cas</span> <span class="hps">s'applique &agrave; vous</span><span>.</span></span></p><p><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Certaines conditions m&eacute;dicales</span> <span class="hps">peuvent interagir avec</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"> </span>Tadapox<span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">.</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span> </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Dites &agrave; votre</span> <span class="hps">m&eacute;decin ou votre pharmacien</span> <span class="hps">si vous</span> <span class="hps">avez des conditions m&eacute;dicales</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">surtout si une des</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">conditions suivantes s'applique &agrave;</span> <span class="hps">vous:</span></span></p><ul><li>si vous prenez une ordonnance ou un m&eacute;dicament en vente libre, une pr&eacute;paration d'herbes ou un suppl&eacute;ment alimentaire</li><li>si vous avez les allergies aux m&eacute;dicaments, aliments ou autres substances</li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">si vous avez</span> <span class="hps">les probl&egrave;mes de cellules</span> <span class="hps">sanguines (par exemple</span><span>, l'an&eacute;mie falciforme</span><span>)</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">si vous</span> <span class="hps">avez des ant&eacute;c&eacute;dents de</span> <span class="hps">probl&egrave;mes h&eacute;patiques ou r&eacute;naux</span><span class="alt-edited">, la pression</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">art&eacute;rielle &eacute;lev&eacute;e ou basse</span><span class="alt-edited">, les ulc&egrave;res,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">les probl&egrave;mes d'</span></span>h&eacute;morragie<span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="alt-edited">, les probl&egrave;mes</span> <span class="hps">cardiaques (par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, l'insuffisance cardiaque,</sp