; votre</span> <span class="hps">m&eacute;decin si </span></span>Tadapox <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">peut interagir</span> <span class="hps">avec d'autres </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">m&eacute;dicaments</span> <span class="hps">que vous prenez.</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">Consultez votre</span> <span class="hps">m&eacute;decin avant de commencer</span><span>, abandonner ou</span> <span class="hps">modifier la dose de</span> <span class="hps">tout m&eacute;dicament.</span></span></p><p><strong>Information de s&eacute;curit&eacute; importante:</strong></p><ul><li>Tadapox <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">peut causer le vertige</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">la somnolence</span><span>, l'&eacute;vanouissement,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">ou une vision floue</span><span>. </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Ces</span> <span class="hps">effets</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">peuvent &ecirc;tre pires si</span> <span class="hps">vous le prenez</span> <span class="hps">avec de l'alcool</span> <span class="hps">ou certains m&eacute;dicaments. </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">Utilisez </span></span>Tadapox <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">avec prudence</span><span>. </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">Ne </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">conduisez pas</span> <span class="hps">une auto ou n'accomplissez pas</span> <span class="hps">d'autres</span> <span class="hps">t&acirc;ches</span> <span class="hps">dangereux jusqu'&agrave; ce que</span> <span class="hps">vous savez comment</span> <span class="hps">vous y r&eacute;agissez</span><span>.</span></span></li><li>Tadapox <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">peut causer le vertige</span> <span class="hps">ou l'&eacute;vanouissement; 